msContents.summary: The diary of Helen Griffith, documenting her time at Bryn Mawr College. In it she describes her day to day schedule including classes she did and did not attend, gossip about friends, and her meal schedule. Occassionally she offers her opinion on whats happening at the college. There are occassional tiime skips with the latter part of the diary documenting her post graduate life.
